      "instruction": "<p><span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>Warm the brie halves</strong></span></p>\n<p>Place the <strong>brie</strong> <span class=\"text-highlight\"><strong>halves</strong></span> onto the <span class=\"text-highlight\">golden</span><strong><span class=\"text-highlight\"> pastry squares</span></strong>, skin-side <span class=\"text-highlight\">up.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Drizzle the <strong>brie</strong> with the <strong>honey</strong>.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Add the <strong>whole grapes</strong> to the other side of the baking tray and drizzle with <strong>olive oil</strong>.</span></p>\n<p><span class=\"text-highlight\">Return the tray to the oven for 10-12 minutes or until the <strong>brie</strong> is bubbling. </span></p>",
